stimulus:
Welcome to the experiment.

Tap "START" to begin.

In this part of the experiment, you will be shown a set of flags corresponding to UN member countries.

You will be asked if you can name the country the flag belongs to.

Tap YES if you recognize to which country the flag belongs to or NO if you do not.

Tap "START" to begin.

You can take a short break now.

Please tap CONTINUE button when you are ready.

Now, you will perform a study session of the items .

Each flag will appear followed by the country name in sets with a short break between sets.

Hit the NEXT button to move on to the next item.

You will practice on the whole list of items 4 times.

Tap "START" to begin.

You can take a short break now.

Please tap CONTINUE button when you are ready.

You can take a short break now.

Please tap CONTINUE button when you are ready.

You can take a short break now.

Please tap CONTINUE button when you are ready.

You can take a short break now.

Please tap CONTINUE button when you are ready.

You can take a short break now.

Please tap CONTINUE button when you are ready.

You can take a short break now.

Please tap CONTINUE button when you are ready.

You can take a short break now.

Please tap CONTINUE button when you are ready.

You can take a short break now.

Please tap CONTINUE button when you are ready.

Now you will be asked if you remember the right name of the country associated to its flag.

Each flag will be shown once and you will click YES if you remember the right name of the country or NO if you do not.

If you answer YES, you will be asked if you are confident on the name of the country. Please click "Completely" if you are absolutely sure you can remember, or "Just Guessing if you are not sure your answer is right".

Tap "START" to begin.

This is the end of the experiment.

Thank you very much for your participation.
